
Privacy Policy
 Ice cream Manager
Last Updated: june 2026
 Icecream Manager respects your privacy. This application is designed to work completely offline and does not collect, store, or share any personal information from users.
1. Information Collection
 Icecream Manager does NOT collect any personal or sensitive user data.
The application:
Does not require user registration
Does not collect names, emails, or phone numbers
Does not track user activity
Does not access device location
Does not use analytics services
2. Local Data Storage
All data entered into the application is stored locally on the user's device only.
This may include:
Products
Flavors
Sales records
Inventory data
Customer information entered manually by the user
No data is transmitted to external servers.
3. Internet Usage
The application works fully offline and does not require an internet connection.
4. Permissions
 Icecream Manager does not request unnecessary device permissions.
5. Data Sharing
We do not sell, share, or transfer any user data to third parties.
6. Security
Since all data is stored locally on the device, users are responsible for protecting access to their devices.
7. Children's Privacy
This application is not directed toward children under the age of 13.
8. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page.
